sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Operator as Operator
    participant Client as MCP Client
    participant Server as VsMcpBridge.McpServer
    participant Tool as VS-backed MCP Tool
    participant PipeClient as PipeClient
    participant Pipe as Named Pipe: VsMcpBridge
    participant VSIX as VSIX Tool Window

    Client->>Server: tools/call vs_propose_text_edit
    Server->>Tool: Invoke VS-backed tool
    Tool->>PipeClient: SendAsync(command, request)
    PipeClient->>Pipe: ConnectAsync(timeout)
    Pipe--xPipeClient: unavailable / timeout
    PipeClient-->>Tool: Success=false activation diagnostic with RequestId
    Tool-->>Server: Error text with activation instructions
    Server-->>Client: Tool response: VS MCP Bridge is not active

    Note over PipeClient,Tool: Diagnostic contains no raw payload or secret-like values.
    Note over Client,Server: MCP initialize and tools/list remain unaffected.

    Operator->>VSIX: Launch VS Experimental Instance
    Operator->>VSIX: View -> Other Windows -> VS MCP Bridge
    VSIX->>Pipe: Start named-pipe side
    Client->>Server: Retry vs_get_active_document
    Server->>Tool: Invoke VS-backed tool
    Tool->>PipeClient: SendAsync(command, request)
    PipeClient->>Pipe: ConnectAsync(timeout)
    Pipe-->>PipeClient: connected
    PipeClient->>VSIX: Write request envelope
    VSIX-->>PipeClient: Return VS response
    PipeClient-->>Tool: Success=true response
    Tool-->>Server: Tool result
    Server-->>Client: Successful VS-backed MCP response
